Houston American Energy to List Shares on Colombian Exchange

-- B y   A n d r e a   J a r a m i l l o
-- 
2011-04-14T13:18:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/houston-american-energy-to-list-shares-on-colombian-exchange.html
Houston American Energy Corp. (HUSA)  said
it plans to list its shares on the Colombian stock exchange.  The company, which trades on the NYSE Amex, said in a
statement yesterday that it is seeking approval from local
authorities to carry out a secondary listing on the exchange
operated by  Bolsa de Valores de Colombia (BVC)  SA.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrea Jaramillo in Bogota at 
 ajaramillo1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at  papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  